@icankeep you are talking about **generic reference**, that is the consumer side generic.
I'm talking about the **generic service**, that is the provider side generic.

Technically, server side can decode the hessian stream to Map/List structure, this can let server side handle the unknown types.

First, avoid scan duplicated packages or sub-package:
```
